Package org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.util

This package contains utility classes and functions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AGCLSyntaxUtil
    Helper class with useful methods for manipulating AGCL syntax
    AGCLUtil
    This class collects general-purpose utility methods for the AGCL analysis tool.
    HashSetFactory
    Concrete set factory that provides sets implemented as HashSet
    PathUtil
    This class provides some auxiliary path manipulation functions.
    SetFactory
    An abstract factory for sets.
    Template
    A minimal template substitution class.
    TemplateManager
    This class is used for loading and providing templates used by the plug-in.
    TreeSetFactory
    Concrete set factory that provides sets implemented as TreeSet (red-black tree)
